		<div class="courseListDescription">This course gives students the practical research methods needed to statistically describe and analyze criminal justice phenomena.  Emphasis throughout the course is on practical uses and application of these techniques to understand criminal justice issues, rather than on their mathematical derivations.</div>
	
	
