    <a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/criminology/CRM/350.html" title="CRM 350 - Cyber Criminology" class="courseListCourseLink"><span class="courseListCourseCode">CRM 350</span> - <span class="courseListCourseName">Cyber Criminology</span></a>
    
	
		<div class="courseListDescription">This course asks critical questions about the nature of crimes (e.g. hacking, pirating, cyber fraud, and online hate and harassment) and criminal justice responses that have emerged as a result of the invention and popularization of technologies such as the computer, internet, and smartphone.</div>
	
	
